Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:21.61,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1240,360)}with a quick-sharp aim\Nand a hunger from deep inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:26.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(40,360)}小熊總是跟著熊媽媽
